{"id": 538, "genre": 1001, "title": "12天没有手机的日子里，你还想给实验者添什么麻烦？", "description": "十一假期实验者将不带手机不做任何攻略去三座从未去过的城市（南京青岛大连），每天我们在读者评论中选取一个可行性比较高的任务让她去完成。", "record_count": 4085, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702200959tBGPoIsajTdbHmnQ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-17T10:01:17Z", "options": [{"id": 12036, "content": "一个人去音乐节假装自己是同性恋一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 170, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143412}, {"id": 12037, "content": "不带现金不带银行卡去饭店吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 511, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113515}, {"id": 14597, "content": "遇见每一个都对他说我爱你，无论男女", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223787}, {"id": 12038, "content": "出行只靠公共交通和电动滑板车", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157780}, {"id": 12039, "content": "关闭一切联系方式生活一个月", "image": null, "praise_count": 129, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168772}, {"id": 12040, "content": "希望这个任务交给赖江锟", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182686}, {"id": 12297, "content": "用你的素颜去约3个人开房", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 180585}, {"id": 12043, "content": "约EX或者初恋。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200750Rqat7JEdzX9L35C1.jpg", "praise_count": 324, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165497}, {"id": 12044, "content": "不带手机的话，当让是去厕所静坐一小时啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 44}, {"id": 12302, "content": "完全不依靠手机发朋友圈求地址，寄明信片给两个好友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191632}, {"id": 12049, "content": "除了写稿子回复评论也不用电脑←_←", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 12051, "content": "不向任何人解释这是个实验(除了最亲密的家人)", "image": null, "praise_count": 407, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 12052, "content": "一天只能和十个人说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 12053, "content": "每天一张自拍照。", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189490}, {"id": 12054, "content": "不用手机，找到一个热门景点", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176866}, {"id": 12057, "content": "不能用手机订票订酒店安排行程 全部用最原始的方式 :)", "image": null, "praise_count": 304, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176577}, {"id": 12313, "content": "去青岛和大连海边静坐一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191693}, {"id": 12058, "content": "说服三个陌生人用他们的手机与你合影，并把照片传给你", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 64424}, {"id": 12059, "content": "每天至少使用一次（不同的）座机电话给不同的朋友打电话（电话号码一定要自己记在心里哦），包括路边的电话亭等付费或是免费的。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211754wLWdROyTxpBnS7Ho.jpg", "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189507}, {"id": 12315, "content": "会不会死", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184584}, {"id": 12060, "content": "去一个完全陌生的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189512}, {"id": 12061, "content": "去一个完全陌生的地方呆上三天", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189512}, {"id": 12062, "content": "跟朋友煲一个小时电话粥", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170038}, {"id": 12064, "content": "找到一些只有当地人能找到的好地方，从礼品店到饭店都可以", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184410}, {"id": 12066, "content": "去大连老铁山，看黄渤海分界线。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142656}, {"id": 13858, "content": "去海边看日出，晒太阳，看风浪，看夕阳，看无边美景", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235050n4EJy2LCd6XwIioh.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211791}, {"id": 12067, "content": "成功向陌生人借手机打电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89616}, {"id": 12068, "content": "寻找三个异性陌生人，分别去他们家借宿三晚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3660}, {"id": 12069, "content": "伪装成同性恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114574}, {"id": 12070, "content": "用陌生人的手机自拍，并收集100张这样的照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 181, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 12326, "content": "绘制这个城市的红灯区地图", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191892}, {"id": 12071, "content": "买一个手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 12072, "content": "不带手机…带着钱和地图，和家人安静地像十年前一样旅游…", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149513}, {"id": 12073, "content": "亲爱的费辣  我初恋去参军了谢谢！约不到！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112725}, {"id": 12329, "content": "和朋友吃饭的时候绝不碰手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109175}, {"id": 12074, "content": "亲爱的们为什么要我伪装成同性恋 我太丑了无法伪装 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112725}, {"id": 12331, "content": "去日本就试了一次，没租Wi-Fi，正好十二天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 190299}, {"id": 12843, "content": "在市中心跟约定的人街头~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149627}, {"id": 12076, "content": "不停地找人说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143057}, {"id": 12332, "content": "上厕所不拿纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119052}, {"id": 12077, "content": "这不叫试验，叫如何为难试验者", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146452}, {"id": 12333, "content": "背出手机里好朋友的号码，并发一条短信。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191945}, {"id": 12846, "content": "去酒吧high一晚，收获肯定很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197191}, {"id": 12079, "content": "对一个陌生人做个互动", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189746}, {"id": 14895, "content": "邀请另外一个人跟你一起加入这个事情，但是不告诉他真像", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228162}, {"id": 12080, "content": "从此再也不能查看家里的情况了~", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235032AtNKo8OkTD703iaU.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66510}, {"id": 12081, "content": "      看着别人玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 185785}, {"id": 12337, "content": "很有意思的样子～尝试一下很爽吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 192043}, {"id": 13105, "content": "不许卖艺卖身卖肾", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202338}, {"id": 12082, "content": "借路人手机每隔二小时给主编发回照片，不能告诉路人是搞活动的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3121}]}